description: Enables programmers to access virtually unlimited number of forex brokersâ€™ price feeds and simultaneously execute orders on all connected terminals. With tick delivery delay not more than 0.1 ms
releaseNotes:
In this release we implement ability to prerecord broker tick-data / read pre-recorded ticks. Updated internal basic Price Engine to provide more realistic price aggregation. You can use internal price engine for guidance purposes only, and you should consider that each broker have different spreads. Output from PE available online via Lexxmt.Forex package (data available with 1.5 second artificial delay).
Also this release contain some minor fixes to API and improved performance.
summary: This is .NET library for multi-terminal  Expert Advisors / automated Forex trading.
title: VisualTradingAPI.com
